Package: compatibleone-coees
Section: net
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, compatibleone (>= ${binary:Version})
Description: CompatibleOne Accords Platform - COEES subsystem
 The CompatibleOne Energy Efficiency Service component is a standalone OCCI
 REST server executable program and must have been started before any
 provisioning plan energy efficiency processing may be performed for the
 provisioning of resources.

Package: compatibleone-cops
Section: net
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, compatibleone (>= ${binary:Version})
Description: CompatibleOne Accords Platform - COPS subsystem
 The CompatibleOne Placement Services module is a standalone OCCI REST server
 executable program and must have been started before any provisioning plan
 smart placement processing may be performed for the provisioning of resources.
 This component is of particular importance as a target or consumer of
 monitoring information in the form of provisioning alerts which will be used
 in the elaboration of the scoring information that will be used to influence
 the selection of particular provider platforms during subsequent placement
 operations.

