Description: CompatibleOne Accords Platform - COIPS subsystem
 COIPS subsystem of the CompatibleOne Accords Platform
 The CompatibleOne Image Production Services module is a standalone OCCI REST
 server executable program and must have been started before any manifest
 parser image production processing may be performed for the provisioning of
 application images for computational resources.

